DOC.brief_summary: This study sought to compare procedural performance of a new coronary stent generation, that is already available in Germany, with hitherto established current drug-eluting stents.
DOC.brief_title: Procedural Advantages of a Novel Drug-Eluting Coronary Stent
DOC.criteria: CAD for PCI, consecutive patients Age under 18 Bare Metal Stents or Scaffolds
